d0031f3c-6b69-4a5c-8913-1c648f54ab7c.title: Shanomi
d0031f3c-6b69-4a5c-8913-1c648f54ab7c.text:
Greetings. Welcome you are in the test of
combat.

options.text: Where do the machines come from?
May I claim my tokens please?

5bc8508e-a634-4311-83b3-0212cd3d8738.title: Shanomi
5bc8508e-a634-4311-83b3-0212cd3d8738.text:
A spare suit of plate armour need you will. Full helm,
plate leggings and platebody yes? Placing it in the
centre of the magical machines you will be doing. KA-
POOF! The armour, it attacks most furiously as if

93ac5aeb-29b6-4421-8a58-1acfd6ae31ed.title: Shanomi
93ac5aeb-29b6-4421-8a58-1acfd6ae31ed.text: alive! Kill it you must, yes.

37ef3dac-c40b-4bd9-b77e-3f1973d1257f.title: <player>
37ef3dac-c40b-4bd9-b77e-3f1973d1257f.text:
So I use a full set of plate armour on the centre plate
of the machines and it will animate it? Then I have to
kill my own armour... how bizarre!

bdf2fed0-7c85-4f75-bb97-bcbc5171480a.title: Shanomi
bdf2fed0-7c85-4f75-bb97-bcbc5171480a.text:
Yes. It is as you are saying. For this earn tokens you
will. Also gain experience in combat you will. Trained
long and hard here have I.

c9e099b2-31dc-422e-b9cd-b6919efc563e.title: <player>
c9e099b2-31dc-422e-b9cd-b6919efc563e.text: So will I lose my armour?

57bb5b17-8b51-4463-9987-c9bdc307ec04.title: Shanomi
57bb5b17-8b51-4463-9987-c9bdc307ec04.text:
Lose armour you will if damaged too much it becomes.
Rare this is, but still possible. If kill you the armour
does, also lose armour you will.

e810fb15-2808-47dd-88b1-4b7e104279f0.title: <player>
e810fb15-2808-47dd-88b1-4b7e104279f0.text:
So, occasionally I might lose a bit because it's being
bashed about and I'll obviously lose it if I die... that it?

f2c2cc0a-d72c-4f3f-b00f-824c611bff4e.title: Shanomi
f2c2cc0a-d72c-4f3f-b00f-824c611bff4e.text: Where do the machines come from?

b1ab43c4-48e7-4a1a-af3d-1fd01416c3a1.title: Shanomi
b1ab43c4-48e7-4a1a-af3d-1fd01416c3a1.text: Make them I did, with magics.

9dd44ab3-f99e-497e-bd58-36c9a08fa904.title: Shanomi
9dd44ab3-f99e-497e-bd58-36c9a08fa904.text:
A skilled warrior also am I. Harrallak mistakes does not
make. Potential in my invention he sees and
opportunity grasps.

6a79d256-95e8-4cd8-80d9-87a0926275a8.title: <player>
6a79d256-95e8-4cd8-80d9-87a0926275a8.text:
I see, so you made the magical machines and Harrallak
saw how they could be used in the guild to train
warrior's combat... interesting. Harrallak certainly is an
intelligent guy.

fb72dc60-fd42-43b6-bec0-1cb0efbee0ac.title: <player>
fb72dc60-fd42-43b6-bec0-1cb0efbee0ac.text: May I claim my tokens please?

0b60da37-db4e-4785-bc25-7ba07d8fe229.title: Shanomi
0b60da37-db4e-4785-bc25-7ba07d8fe229.text:
No tokens earned have you. In training activities
participate you must.

c2b9924c-5a20-4453-ad50-ed5cfed10574.title: <player>
c2b9924c-5a20-4453-ad50-ed5cfed10574.text:
Okay, I'll go see what I can find to do around here to
earn some tokens.
